    dc:creator "Chanabun, Ratmanee; Sutcharit, Chirasak; Tongkerd, Piyoros; Panha, Somsak" ;
    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "The semi-aquatic freshwater earthworms of the genus Glyphidrilus Horst, 1889 from Thailand (Oligochaeta, Almidae) with re-descriptions of several species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/27634>, <https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/27635>, <https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/27652> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/27634>
    dc:description "Figure 19. Photographs showing the A and B type locality of Glyphidrilus borealis sp. n. (arrow head), a muddy swamp near Maeklang Waterfall, Doi Inthanon National Park, Chiangmai and C coloration of newly collected paratype CUMZ 3224 just after the first preservation step in 30 % (v / v) ethanol." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/27634" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/27635>
    dc:description "Figure 20. Morphology of the holotype (CUMZ 3223) of Glyphidrilus borealis sp. n., showing the A external ventral and B internal dorsal views and C paratype specimens showing variation of genital markings location." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/27635" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/27652>
    dc:description "Figure 37. Distribution map of the new Glyphidrilus species from Thailand. Open triangle: Glyphidrilus borealis sp. n., Filled triangle: Glyphidrilus vangthongensis sp. n., Filled star: Glyphidrilus chaophraya sp. n., Open square: Glyphidrilus chiensis sp. n., Filled square: Glyphidrilus quadratus sp. n., Open circle: Glyphidrilus huailuangensis sp. n." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/27652" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

